snippet.title: Top 5 Unknowns
snippet.description:
Welcome to the Top5Unknowns' channel!

We post videos that are related to the paranormal and bring in fun facts for people to learn.

Our channel also aims to educate and bring awareness on cases that are usually not covered on mainstream platforms by compiling 5 findings, which are all referenced.
